727217f-a.text:
Liberty Avenue, north side, between Remington Street and Lloyd Road, viewing east toward the latter and showing an old frame house.  In Wolverton's 1891 map it appears near the Jamaica village corporation line in an area sparsely inhabited.  It may have been a road hotel.

P. L. Sperr

January 28, 1931
